text: Department of the Treasury Internal Revenue Service
This transmits obsolete IRM 22.41.1, Indian Tribal Governments, Outreach.

IRM 22.41.1 contained the procedures for customer education and outreach programs for Indian Tribal Governments specialists who work with Indian tribal governments. IRM 22.41.1 is obsolete because TEGE has a desk guide for outreach and education and all functions will follow the procedures in this desk guide. Accordingly, ITG will follow the procedures set forth in the TEGE desk guide.
IRM 22.41.1, Indian Tribal Governments Outreach, dated December 23, 2016, is obsolete as of the date of this transmittal.
Tax Exempt and Government Entities (TE/GE) Indian Tribal Governments
